name: Destroy and Build
description:
Esperando encontrarme desnuda ante mis males recitando mantras contra insomnio cuento mis lunares para recordar que existo resisto a mis impulsos oscilando en el abismo reconociendo el espejismo del ego equilibrado

-----------------------------------------------

Hoping to find myself naked before my ills reciting mantras against insomnia I count my moles to remember that I exist I resist my impulses oscillating in the abyss recognizing the mirage of the balanced ego


PH. Mariana Samsa
